    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> in half, widthways</p><p>Add the <strong>basa pieces</strong> to a large bowl with your <strong>soy sauce</strong> and set aside to marinate</p>",
