      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s] </strong>in half</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>brioche halves</strong>, cut-side down, and cook for 3 min or until coloured and charred on one side only</p><p>Once charred, remove and set aside until serving and reserve the pan</p>",
