    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and dice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>finely</p><p>Cut your <strong>cucumber </strong>in half lengthways, scoop out the core using a teaspoon, then dice finely</p><p>Wash and shred your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper</p>",
