    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the wedges are almost ready, return the reserved pan to a high heat with a very generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once very hot, add the<strong> coated basa</strong> and cook for 3-4 min on each side or until golden and crisp – this is your <strong>crispy basa</strong></p>",
