    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble the burger, add a little <strong>homemade zingy slaw</strong> to each <strong>charred</strong> <strong>brioche base</strong> and top with the <strong>crispy basa</strong> and <strong>charred</strong> <strong>brioche lid</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>wedges</strong> and any <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>homemade zingy slaw</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
